Space    : Pause and playback resume
Q        : Exit
0        : volume increase
9        : volume reduction
→        : 10 seconds fast forward
←        : back 10 seconds winding
↑        : 1 minute fast forward
↓        : back 1 minute winding
PageUp   : 10 minutes fast forward
PageDown : back 10 minutes winding
M        : audio mute.
######################################
